liner, Clyde trustees\nwill spend $170,000 in widening and\ndeepening the Clyde at Clydebank,\nScotland.\nFOOT BALL ROUND-UP\nSET FOR NOVEMBER 22\nUniversities\u2019 Committee Considers\nArrangement for End-of-\nSeason Event\nThe annual Big Ten Round-Up, a\ndance and festival, to celebrate the con\nclusion of the foot ball season for the\nteams of the Western Conference will\nbe held on Saturday night, November\n22, It was announced today, at a place\nto be decided later.\nA committee composed of representa\ntives of the ten universities, who are\nliving in Washington met Monday to\nconsider preliminary arrangements, and\nfurther announcements will be forth\ncoming later.\nEarl S. Hoffman, president of the Big\nTen, and Miss Nell Ingels, secretary, to\ngether with two representatives from\neach member university, comprise the\ncommittee In charge.\nOnly 500 Americans are now living in\nTurkey.\nLANSBURGH'S\n7th, Bth and E St*.\u2014National 9800\nNo Connection With Any Other Store\nFRANCHETTE\nc\nAnswers the Call\nFor Apparel of\nTrue Individuality\nDress to suit your type\nyour personality that\u2019s the\nsmart thing to do this season!\nPresented are two very new and\nsmart Franchette fashions B\nboth individual and charming! JHHF\nFranchette Fashions Are Exclu- l\nand always delightfully different B\nfrom any other dresses you see at B\nthis price! Cantons, satins and fl\ntransparent velvets in black and Fall\ncolors. Sizes 14 to 46. A*''*\nMr jj Jr-f' jHI *V~\nJwSESr\nJiFfjr\nand always the ultimate\nskillful tailoring and chic! You\u2019ll\nlook your best in a Franchette\nbecause they are subtly fitted to\naccent the slimness of waist and\nhips and laden with the\nj/l season\u2019s most flattering furs!\nill Fashion Shops\u2014Second Floor\nMeet Your Every Need With a\nFranchette Bag\nnew Fran\nchette bag it\nsmart? Os black or brown \"\u2019f J\u00a7sjgpPf^\nmorocco with an in-\nterestingly cut flap weight\ned down with a crystal ball!\nMany more just as fasci